    "macroSummary": "Markets are consolidating gains with S&P 500 near records while geopolitical tensions create cross-currents - oil steady despite Iran war risks, dollar weakening after 7-session decline, and housing data showing continued stress from elevated rates and material cost uncertainty. Energy inventories drew more than expected while crypto shows resilience with Bitcoin holding above key support and analysts calling mini-winter over.",
